{"id":"songs","term":"Songs","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Of Moses (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 15\">Ex. 15</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 21:17\">Num. 21:17</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Deuteronomy 32\">Deut. 32</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 15:3\">Rev. 15:3</a>), Deborah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 5\">Judg. 5</a>), Hannah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Samuel 2\">1 Sam. 2</a>), David (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 22\">2 Sam. 22</a>, and Psalms), Mary (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 1:46\">Luke 1:46-55</a>), Zacharias (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 1:68\">Luke 1:68-79</a>), the angels (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 2:13\">Luke 2:13</a>), Simeon (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 2:29\">Luke 2:29</a>), the redeemed (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 5:9\">Rev. 5:9</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 6:5\">19</a>), Solomon (see SOLOMON, SONGS OF).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Exodus 15","Numbers 21:17","Deuteronomy 32","Revelation 15:3","Judges 5","1 Samuel 2","2 Samuel 22","Luke 1:46","Luke 1:68","Luke 2:13","Luke 2:29","Revelation 5:9","Revelation 6:5"]}